name: Birth-day
description: I make not-so-traditional mandalas. This is one of them. Each one has a very specific energy and intention put into it. You can use it as a wallpaper on your screen or print it out and hang it on your wall and it will have positive effect on your psyche. Since it is my first ever upload/nft, it is called birth-day. The light that broke the mirror and out came the rose :)
